58:06.480 --> 58:07.740
Woman:
Bessie, no!

58:07.980 --> 58:09.510
(Chatter continues)

58:15.390 --> 58:17.290
Get on out of here!

58:17.560 --> 58:18.620
What the hell
are you doing?

58:18.860 --> 58:20.790
- Get back.
- Hey!

58:21.130 --> 58:22.930
You better pick up
your sheets and run!

58:23.230 --> 58:24.730
- (Gunshot)
- <i>(crowd screams)</i>

58:26.700 --> 58:28.600
Get out of here.
I'm gonna get you!

58:28.870 --> 58:30.170
Bessie:
<i>Get out of here!</i>

58:31.640 --> 58:35.570
<i>We'll be back!</i>
<i>(Cackles)</i>

58:37.210 --> 58:38.680
<i>We'll be back!</i>

